text: Eva Henning (born Eva Wetlesen; 10 May 1920 – 18 April 2016) was a Swedish stage and movie actress. She was known for her roles in Elvira Madigan (1943), Flickan från tredje raden (1949), and in The Firebird (1952). She was born in Newark, New York to Swedish parents. Henning died in Oslo, Norway on 18 April 2016, aged 95. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1920 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Swedish movie actors Category:Swedish television actors Category:Actors from New York (state)
